wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"competing nations\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Green Games\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"the environmental cost\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"those nations\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"the science\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Temperatures are expected to soar again in the European summer after setting records in 2023, but there will be no air conditioning in the athletes' rooms at Paris 2024, which has pledged to host the \\\"greenest ever\\\" Games.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Temperatures\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"the European summer\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"no air conditioning\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' rooms\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"greenest ever\\\" Games\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, buildings in the athletes' village have been designed with a cooling system drawing water from underground and facades orientated so they get little direct sun.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"a cooling system\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"little direct sun\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This village was designed to avoid the need for air conditioning, even in very, very high temperatures, in order to maintain comfortable temperatures,\\\" Hidalgo told Reuters on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This village\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"very, very high temperatures\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"comfortable temperatures\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"Hidalgo\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Bach (L), president of the International Olympic Committee, visits the Paris 2024 Olympic Village construction site in Paris, France, December 1, 2023.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"L\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP With climate scientists warning that global warming has produced more extreme weather patterns in much of the world, organizers of Paris 2024 have said they want to halve the carbon footprint compared with the Rio 2016 and London 2012 Summer Games.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://db