_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And secondly, we have to trust the scientists when they help us to construct buildings in a sober way that allows us to make do without air conditioning.\\\"\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scientists\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"a sober way\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's President Emmanuel Macron (2nd L) visits the Paris 2024 Olympic Village in Paris, France, February 29, 2024.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1887, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\":