bpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9645919914672344e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2933, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 2952, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995946896750402, \"rank\": 0.0002022874671797372, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A view\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a bedroom\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' apartments\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP What matters for Hidalgo, however, is that the athletes' village, which will be home to some 6,000 Parisiens after the Games, is a sustainable project.\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9997171859671096, \"rank\": 0.0002828940394572381, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/CFP\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"some 6,000 Parisiens\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"a sustainable project\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But then they do what they want; I am not going to tell them what to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What matters to me is that these buildings, these flats will become a neighborhood where people from L'Ile-Saint-Denis, Saint-Ouen and Saint-Denis (in the Paris suburbs) will live.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these buildings\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3274}, {\"ngram\": \"these flats\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"a neighborhood\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"L'Ile-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Ouen\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These new buildings will not need air conditioning, so we are working for the long term.\\\"\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These new buildings\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3432}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"the long term\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lending support to the organizers' vision, several other delegations have said they fully trust they will not need air conditioning at the Games.\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3519}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers' vision\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"several other delegations\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have visited the Olympic Village in Paris regularly in the last years and rate the clever cooling system installed in floor and ceiling to be sufficient for the climate zone,\\\" the German Olympic Committee told Reuters.\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3672, \"end\": 3687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1780697293344318e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 3691, \"end\": 3696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.51720716045298e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3835, \"end\": 3859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"German Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Olympic_Sports_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 3865, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999974571033408, \"rank\": 2.54290296923881e-06, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour